{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Or they-- a lot of people say that they made the people dig their own graves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they killed them and threw them in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know which way it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Me and my husband, in, in the, the-- this was about 20 people, maybe less, working there by the turf and by the lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were all there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do because the Polish people started to say that they-- catching the Jews again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That particular day, I had a very bad day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I went to pick up my portion for the day, a piece of bread and some coffee or something, whatever they gave you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had my little cousin with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And she ran away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [CRYING] [SOBBING] Whenever I think about her, it's killing me because she could have been alive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She ran back to her mother because her mother was working where they were packing those clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She said she wanted to see her mother again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And I thought-- this was Friday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I thought, Sunday, I'm going to go back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I'm going to get her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was so-- [CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Then we were hiding in the lumberyard for a few days, for Friday, Saturday, and Sunday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then Monday, we knew they're gong to come work in the lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we went-- we ran out from the lumber yard, and we went, went into the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was another few people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, we're going to go back to Jelnica.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, why are we going back to Jelnica?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The man says, there's a Polish man that hides Jews there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went back there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
